data.description: WELCOME TO THE PALMEROSA!!! This private oasis of tranquility will leave you feeling nostalgic, peaceful, and calm. Boasting over 12 acres, this property includes a custom built house with all your modern day amenities. Sit on the front porch, and get lost in the relaxing sounds of all things county. If you listen closely you can hear the birds chirping, the bullfrogs croaking, and the squirrels busy at work. Once you've finished your relaxation in the sun, step into a custom built home that boasts a huge primary suite, with a separate shower, and jetted soaking tub. Each of the 5 bedrooms boast walk in closets. There is also a bathroom conveniently located next to each bedroom, with 2 bedrooms sharing a jack and jill bath. The kitchen is one of every chef's dreams, with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a breakfast nook, and separate formal dining. This beauty opens up to the den, which is perfect for entertaining. Once everyone has arrived, open the French doors that lead to the formal dining, and let the meals, laughter, memories, and companionship overflow..  This home is SPECTACULAR, with too many great points to mention. Please call the listing agent, so you may bask in the glory of the beauty for yourself.
